// Changing Keyboard Layout from Terminal
// HPH Knowledgebase -RasPi
// Fluvio L. Lobo Fenoglietto

// Follow this guide to change the keyboard layout, by country code, from the command terminal

1. In the terminal, type:

> setxkbmap [2 letter country code]

For instance,

> setxkbmap us
 
